	mposed of over two million items.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nCentral Library\n\n
	Room Location: Level 8 - Gallery\n\nRegistration Required: Registration is
	 not required.\n\nDetailed Description: Enjoy viewing books\, ephemera\, a
	rt\, and more at our exhibit in the Level 8 Gallery between January 23\, 2
	026 and April 11\, 2026.\, Thanks to our sponsor\n\nThe Seattle Public Lib
	rary Foundation .\n\nEvent Logistics:\n\nFind out about Exhibits.\n\nConta
	ct Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us\n\nor call 206-3
